item.description: We're going to discuss some new rules for our group's political action committee as well as how we can use it in the future. We'll also be discussing possible future events, including one that's in the works for Jan. 5th in New Hampshire. Any other new ideas are welcome as well.
item.how_to_find_us: Call me at 508-308-9008 if you have any problems.
item.why: Join us, because Sunday's event was so successful, and we want to do it again in New Hampshire!
item.name: Organizational / PAC Meeting
